00w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Olive.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Olive-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth UDH green\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Olive-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Olive-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Olive-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Olive-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Olive.webp 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Gold.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Gold-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth UDH gole\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Gold-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Gold-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Gold-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Gold-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Gold.webp 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Espresso.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Espresso-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth UDH brown\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Espresso-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Espresso-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Espresso-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Espresso-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Espresso.webp 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Blue.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Blue-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth UDH blue\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Blue-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Blue-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Blue-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Blue-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Blue.webp 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Black.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Black-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth UDH black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Black-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Black-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Black-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Black-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth_UDH-Black.webp 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Maybe more importantly for the fashion-conscious out there, the hanger includes a Color Shop anodized bolt and washer. These are available in nine different anodized colors to match the other WTC components and accessories including raw silver, red, gold, orange, black, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-copmonents-olive-color-parts/\" target=\"_blank\">olive</a>, blue, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wtc-ultraviolet-purple-bike-parts/\" target=\"_blank\">ultraviolet purple</a>, and espresso. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/UDH_Grease_Color_1024x1024.png.webp\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"464\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/UDH_Grease_Color_1024x1024.png.webp\" alt=\"WTC UDH hanger installation guide\n\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/UDH_Grease_Color_1024x1024.png.webp 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/UDH_Grease_Color_1024x1024.png-297x135.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/UDH_Grease_Color_1024x1024.png-120x54.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/UDH_Grease_Color_1024x1024.png-768x348.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Compatible with all UDH bikes running standard derailleurs, the hanger has a claimed weight of 32g and an M12x1.0 axle thread pitch. The WTC UDH sells for $44.95</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/products/universal-derailleur-hanger-udh\" target=\"_blank\"><em>wolftoothcomponents.com</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-components-universal-derailleur-hanger-udh-replacement-color/\">Wolf Tooth Components Adds Color &amp; Precision to New Universal Derailleur Hanger</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"341628f6e7ea4df0550216155517cae7e1a37dcf45071f852c5141a92342ff21","category":"Cycling"}